ome. You can check your swing on VR by holding the controller instead of the golf club and swinging. You can also set the controller on a golf club for practice and swing. In that case, use the position adjustment function of the controller.", "short_description": "An application for golf practice that can be used at home. You can keep hitting golf in the VR space, and you can objectively check your swing. This will be a beta version for testing.\n\nPlease note that this application is a beta version, so adjustments for swing and ballistic behavior have not been completed."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "vrg_e003_tate.png", "id": "2730464913921008", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75404390_2730464917254341_5136702418237828326_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jqVJ-ucDtBYQ7kNvgHbm04T&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAXaFatOMrE2Ys4b3QXqLLfZTTaLNEmsANBH_VBqSZ1eA&oe=67011754"}, {"file_name": "vrg_e003_icon.png", "id": "554821149020375", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75292491_554821152353708_2328777657735194110_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4W03qGm-I5gQ7kNvgH67bB9&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAvEK48gYhsGfEuL6ivFI8hGzFanY4C97uh1Bc5r0AV_g&oe=67013170"}, {"file_name": "vrg_e003_yoko.png", "id": "522206015649103", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75422375_522206018982436_1386274127943337803_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=-7LcZMrJEnYQ7kNvgHJdlvX&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCWoLwtyiw5SOmQwZSajyrLzIAQGQczk9EXw_IlrTYwyg&oe=670126FC"}, {"file_name": "vrg_e003_squea.png", "id": "336652144498910", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75375764_336652147832243_7690546353479640304_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=